---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Pricing">
  <div class="container">
    <section class="hero">
      <h1>Simple, Transparent Pricing</h1>
      <p class="lead">
        Choose the plan that's right for your organization's unique needs.
        Every plan includes our core platform capabilities.
      </p>
    </section>

    <section class="section">
      <div class="pricing-grid">
        <div class="pricing-card">
          <h3>Starter</h3>
          <div class="pricing-price">Free</div>
          <p class="pricing-desc">It's not a trial &mdash; it's a starting point. Perfect for teams looking to explore the power of AI-driven collaboration.</p>
          <ul class="pricing-features">
            <li>Up to 5 team members</li>
            <li>Basic analytics dashboard</li>
            <li>Community support</li>
            <li>100 actionable insights per month</li>
            <li>Standard integrations</li>
          </ul>
          <a href="#" class="btn btn-secondary pricing-btn">Get Started</a>
        </div>

        <div class="pricing-card pricing-popular">
          <span class="popular-badge">Most Popular</span>
          <h3>Pro</h3>
          <div class="pricing-price">&pound;49<span>/month</span></div>
          <p class="pricing-desc">For teams that are serious about leveraging AI-driven insights to drive meaningful results.</p>
          <ul class="pricing-features">
            <li>Unlimited team members</li>
            <li>Advanced analytics suite</li>
            <li>Priority support</li>
            <li>Unlimited actionable insights</li>
            <li>Premium integrations</li>
            <li>Custom workflows</li>
          </ul>
          <a href="#" class="btn btn-primary pricing-btn">Get Started</a>
        </div>

        <div class="pricing-card">
          <h3>Enterprise</h3>
          <div class="pricing-price">Custom</div>
          <p class="pricing-desc">This isn't a plan &mdash; it's a partnership. For organizations that need a holistic, tailored solution.</p>
          <ul class="pricing-features">
            <li>Everything in Pro</li>
            <li>Dedicated success manager</li>
            <li>Enterprise-grade SLA</li>
            <li>Holistic security audit</li>
            <li>Bespoke onboarding</li>
          </ul>
          <a href="#" class="btn btn-secondary pricing-btn">Get Started</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="section">
      <div class="faq">
        <h2 class="section-title text-center">Frequently Asked Questions</h2>
        <div class="faq-list">
          <div class="faq-item">
            <h3>Can I try SynergyFlow before committing?</h3>
            <p>
              Absolutely! Our Starter plan is completely free and gives you access to
              our core features. We don't ask you to take our word for it &mdash; we ask
              you to experience the transformative power of our platform for yourself.
            </p>
          </div>
          <div class="faq-item">
            <h3>What makes Pro the most popular choice?</h3>
            <p>
              Our Pro plan offers the optimal balance of cutting-edge features and value.
              It's designed for teams that are serious about leveraging AI-driven insights
              to drive meaningful results &mdash; it's not just an upgrade, it's a
              transformation.
            </p>
          </div>
          <div class="faq-item">
            <h3>How does Enterprise pricing work?</h3>
            <p>
              Enterprise isn't about scale &mdash; it's about depth. We aim to work
              closely with your team to create a bespoke solution that delivers maximum
              value across every facet of your operations.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
  </div>
</Layout>

<style>
  .pricing-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
    gap: 1.5rem;
    align-items: start;
  }

  .pricing-card {
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    border-radius: 8px;
    padding: 2rem 1.5rem;
    text-align: center;
    position: relative;
    background: var(--bg-card);
  }

  .pricing-popular {
    border-color: var(--accent);
    box-shadow: 0 0 0 1px var(--accent);
  }

  .popular-badge {
    position: absolute;
    top: -12px;
    left: 50%;
    transform: translateX(-50%);
    background: var(--accent);
    color: #ffffff;
    font-size: 0.75rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    padding: 0.25rem 0.75rem;
    border-radius: 20px;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.05em;
  }

  .pricing-card h3 {
    font-size: 1.25rem;
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }

  .pricing-price {
    font-size: 2.5rem;
    font-weight: 800;
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }

  .pricing-price span {
    font-size: 1rem;
    font-weight: 400;
    color: var(--text-muted);
  }

  .pricing-desc {
    color: var(--text-muted);
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
  }

  .pricing-features {
    list-style: none;
    text-align: left;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
  }

  .pricing-features li {
    padding: 0.4rem 0;
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    color: var(--text-secondary);
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border-light);
  }

  .pricing-btn {
    width: 100%;
    text-align: center;
  }

  .faq {
    max-width: 700px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .faq-list {
    margin-top: 2rem;
  }

  .faq-item {
    padding: 1.25rem 0;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
  }

  .faq-item h3 {
    font-size: 1.05rem;
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }

  .faq-item p {
    color: var(--text-secondary);
    font-size: 0.95rem;
    line-height: 1.7;
  }
</style>
